data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Make sure the server you join is in the region of the world you live in! (i.e West US, East US, Europe, etc). If you have a problem where you can't see your character, REGENERATE YOUR PLAYER ID THEN REJOIN THE SERVER. If you tried to connect to the server and you get an error, REJOIN THE SERVER.
